#. <section class="sutta" id="mn15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn15:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 15"
msgstr "Middle Discourses 15"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn15:0.2"
msgid "Anumānasutta"
msgstr "Measuring Up"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya1"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. VAR: susumāragire → suṃsumāragire (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "mn15:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhaggesu viharati susumāragire "
"bhesakaḷāvane migadāye."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Mahāmoggallāna was staying in the land of the Bhaggas "
"on Crocodile Hill, in the deer park at Bhesakaḷā’s Wood."

msgctxt "mn15:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There Venerable Mahāmoggallāna addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "mn15:1.4"
msgid "“āvuso bhikkhavo”ti."
msgstr "“Reverends, mendicants!”"

msgctxt "mn15:1.5"
msgid "“Āvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Reverend,” they replied."

msgctxt "mn15:1.6"
msgid "Āyasmā mahāmoggallāno etadavoca:"
msgstr "Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya2"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:2.1"
msgid "“Pavāreti cepi, āvuso, bhikkhu:"
msgstr "“Suppose a mendicant invites"

msgctxt "mn15:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘vadantu maṃ āyasmanto, vacanīyomhi āyasmantehī’ti, so ca hoti dubbaco, "
"dovacassakaraṇehi dhammehi samannāgato, akkhamo appadakkhiṇaggāhī "
"anusāsaniṃ, atha kho naṃ sabrahmacārī na ceva vattabbaṃ maññanti, na ca "
"anusāsitabbaṃ maññanti, na ca tasmiṃ puggale vissāsaṃ āpajjitabbaṃ maññanti."
msgstr ""
"other mendicants to admonish them. But they’re hard to admonish, having "
"qualities that make them hard to admonish. They're impatient, and don't take "
"instruction respectfully. So their spiritual companions don’t think it’s "
"worth advising and instructing them, and that person doesn’t gain their "
"trust."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya3"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.1"
msgid "Katame cāvuso, dovacassakaraṇā dhammā?"
msgstr "And what are the qualities that make them hard to admonish?"

msgctxt "mn15:3.2"
msgid "Idhāvuso, bhikkhu pāpiccho hoti, pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gato."
msgstr ""
"Firstly, a mendicant has wicked desires, having fallen under the sway of "
"wicked desires."

msgctxt "mn15:3.3"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu pāpiccho hoti, pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gato—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.4"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (1)"
msgstr "This is a quality that makes them difficult to admonish."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.5"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu attukkaṃsako hoti paravambhī."
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant glorifies themselves and puts others down. …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.6"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu attukkaṃsako hoti paravambhī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.7"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.8"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu kodhano hoti kodhābhibhūto."
msgstr "They’re angry, overcome by anger …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.9"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu kodhano hoti kodhābhibhūto—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.10"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.11"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu kodhano hoti kodhahetu upanāhī."
msgstr "They’re angry, and hostile due to anger …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.12"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu kodhano hoti kodhahetu upanāhī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.13"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.14"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu kodhano hoti kodhahetu abhisaṅgī."
msgstr "They’re angry, and stubborn due to anger …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.15"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu kodhano hoti kodhahetu abhisaṅgī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.16"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
#. VAR: kodhasāmantā → kodhasāmantaṃ (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "mn15:3.17"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu kodhano hoti kodhasāmantā vācaṃ nicchāretā."
msgstr "They’re angry, and blurt out words bordering on anger …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.18"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu kodhano hoti kodhasāmantā vācaṃ nicchāretā—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.19"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
#. VAR: codito → cudito (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "mn15:3.20"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakaṃ paṭippharati."
msgstr "When accused, they object to the accuser …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.21"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakaṃ paṭippharati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.22"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.23"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakaṃ apasādeti."
msgstr "When accused, they rebuke the accuser …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.24"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakaṃ apasādeti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.25"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (8)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.96"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.26"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakassa paccāropeti."
msgstr "When accused, they retort to the accuser …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.27"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakassa paccāropeti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.28"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (9)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.29"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena aññenaññaṃ paṭicarati, bahiddhā "
"kathaṃ apanāmeti, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti."
msgstr ""
"When accused, they dodge the issue, distract the discussion with irrelevant "
"points, and display irritation, hate, and bitterness …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.30"
msgid ""
"Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena aññenaññaṃ paṭicarati, bahiddhā kathaṃ "
"apanāmeti, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.31"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (10)"
msgstr ""

# apadana has the root meaning of “reaping, harvest”, hence the more common sense of “story of past lives, i.e. deeds and their consequences”.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.32"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena apadāne na sampāyati."
msgstr "When accused, they don’t accept the consequences of their deeds …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.33"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena apadāne na sampāyati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.34"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (11)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.35"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu makkhī hoti paḷāsī."
msgstr "They are offensive and contemptuous …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.36"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu makkhī hoti paḷāsī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.37"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (12)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.38"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu issukī hoti maccharī."
msgstr "They’re envious and stingy …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.39"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu issukī hoti maccharī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.40"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (13)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.41"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu saṭho hoti māyāvī."
msgstr "They’re devious and deceitful …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.42"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu saṭho hoti māyāvī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.43"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (14)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.44"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu thaddho hoti atimānī."
msgstr "They’re obstinate and vain …"

msgctxt "mn15:3.45"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu thaddho hoti atimānī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.46"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (15)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.47"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī hoti ādhānaggāhī "
"duppaṭinissaggī."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant is attached to their own views, holding them tight, "
"and refusing to let go."

msgctxt "mn15:3.48"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī hoti ādhānaggāhī duppaṭinissaggī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:3.49"
msgid "ayampi dhammo dovacassakaraṇo. (16)"
msgstr "This too is a quality that makes them difficult to admonish."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:3.50"
msgid "Ime vuccantāvuso, dovacassakaraṇā dhammā."
msgstr "These are the qualities that make them hard to admonish."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:4.1"
msgid "No cepi, āvuso, bhikkhu pavāreti:"
msgstr "Suppose a mendicant doesn’t invite"

msgctxt "mn15:4.2"
msgid ""
"‘vadantu maṃ āyasmanto, vacanīyomhi āyasmantehī’ti, so ca hoti suvaco, "
"sovacassakaraṇehi dhammehi samannāgato, khamo padakkhiṇaggāhī anusāsaniṃ, "
"atha kho naṃ sabrahmacārī vattabbañceva maññanti, anusāsitabbañca maññanti, "
"tasmiñca puggale vissāsaṃ āpajjitabbaṃ maññanti."
msgstr ""
"other mendicants to admonish them. But they’re easy to admonish, having "
"qualities that make them easy to admonish. They're accepting, and take "
"instruction respectfully. So their spiritual companions think it’s worth "
"advising and instructing them, and that person gains their trust."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya5"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.1"
msgid "Katame cāvuso, sovacassakaraṇā dhammā?"
msgstr "And what are the qualities that make them easy to admonish?"

msgctxt "mn15:5.2"
msgid "Idhāvuso, bhikkhu na pāpiccho hoti, na pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gato."
msgstr "Firstly, a mendicant doesn’t have wicked desires …"

msgctxt "mn15:5.3"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu na pāpiccho hoti na pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gato—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.4"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (1)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.5"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu anattukkaṃsako hoti aparavambhī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.6"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu anattukkaṃsako hoti aparavambhī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.7"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.8"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu na kodhano hoti na kodhābhibhūto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.9"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu na kodhano hoti na kodhābhibhūto—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.10"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc24"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.11"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu na kodhano hoti na kodhahetu upanāhī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.12"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu na kodhano hoti na kodhahetu upanāhī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.13"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc25"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.14"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu na kodhano hoti na kodhahetu abhisaṅgī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.15"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu na kodhano hoti na kodhahetu abhisaṅgī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.16"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc26"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.17"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu na kodhano hoti na kodhasāmantā vācaṃ "
"nicchāretā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.18"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu na kodhano hoti na kodhasāmantā vācaṃ nicchāretā—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.19"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc27"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.20"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakaṃ nappaṭippharati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.21"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakaṃ nappaṭippharati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.22"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.97"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc28"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.23"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakaṃ na apasādeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.24"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakaṃ na apasādeti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.25"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (8)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc29"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.26"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakassa na paccāropeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.27"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena codakassa na paccāropeti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.28"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (9)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc30"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.29"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena na aññenaññaṃ paṭicarati, na "
"bahiddhā kathaṃ apanāmeti, na kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.30"
msgid ""
"Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena na aññenaññaṃ paṭicarati, na bahiddhā "
"kathaṃ apanāmeti, na kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.31"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (10)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc31"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.32"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena apadāne sampāyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.33"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu codito codakena apadāne sampāyati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.34"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (11)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc32"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.35"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu amakkhī hoti apaḷāsī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.36"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu amakkhī hoti apaḷāsī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.37"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (12)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc33"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.38"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu anissukī hoti amaccharī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.39"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu anissukī hoti amaccharī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.40"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (13)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc34"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.41"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu asaṭho hoti amāyāvī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.42"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu asaṭho hoti amāyāvī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.43"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (14)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc35"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.44"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu atthaddho hoti anatimānī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.45"
msgid "Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu atthaddho hoti anatimānī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.46"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (15)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc36"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.47"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu asandiṭṭhiparāmāsī hoti anādhānaggāhī "
"suppaṭinissaggī."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant isn’t attached to their own views, not holding them "
"tight, but letting them go easily."

msgctxt "mn15:5.48"
msgid ""
"Yaṃpāvuso, bhikkhu asandiṭṭhiparāmāsī hoti, anādhānaggāhī suppaṭinissaggī—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:5.49"
msgid "ayampi dhammo sovacassakaraṇo. (16)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc37"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:5.50"
msgid "Ime vuccantāvuso, sovacassakaraṇā dhammā."
msgstr "These are the qualities that make them easy to admonish."

# Anumana seems to only occur twice in the EBTs, here and SN 22.36. There, BB accepts the sense “measure against”. It seems to me this meaning applies here. the passage specifically discusses, not an inference in general, but how one is to measure oneself against another. This, of course, reads straight from the etymology of the term. Moreover, this sense makes the whole sutta hang together better. The next section refers to paccavekkhana, i.e. “reflection”. So this section is about an external standard, the next section is about an inner standard. In later texts, especially Mil 6.4.1, anumana did indeed come to mean “inference”.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya6"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc38"></a>
#. VAR: anuminitabbaṃ → anumānitabbaṃ (s1-3)
msgctxt "mn15:6.1"
msgid "Tatrāvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ anuminitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"In such a case, a mendicant should measure themselves against another like "
"this."

msgctxt "mn15:6.2"
msgid ""
"‘yo khvāyaṃ puggalo pāpiccho, pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gato, ayaṃ me puggalo "
"appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""
"‘This person has wicked desires, having fallen under the sway of wicked "
"desires. And I don’t like or approve of this person."

msgctxt "mn15:6.3"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho panassaṃ pāpiccho pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gato, ahampāssaṃ "
"paresaṃ appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""
"And if I were to fall under the sway of wicked desires, others wouldn’t like "
"or approve of me.’"

msgctxt "mn15:6.4"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘na pāpiccho bhavissāmi, na pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ "
"vasaṃ gato’ti cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (1)"
msgstr ""
"A mendicant who knows this should give rise to the thought: ‘I will not fall "
"under the sway of wicked desires.’ …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc39"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.5"
msgid ""
"‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo attukkaṃsako paravambhī, ayaṃ me puggalo appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.6"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho panassaṃ attukkaṃsako paravambhī, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ appiyo "
"amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.7"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘anattukkaṃsako bhavissāmi aparavambhī’ti "
"cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc40"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.8"
msgid ""
"‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo kodhano kodhābhibhūto, ayaṃ me puggalo appiyo amanāpo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.9"
msgid ""
"Ahañceva kho panassaṃ kodhano kodhābhibhūto, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ appiyo "
"amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.10"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘na kodhano bhavissāmi na kodhābhibhūto’ti "
"cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc41"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.11"
msgid ""
"‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo kodhano kodhahetu upanāhī, ayaṃ me puggalo appiyo "
"amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.12"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho panassaṃ kodhano kodhahetu upanāhī, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ appiyo "
"amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.13"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘na kodhano bhavissāmi na kodhahetu upanāhī’ti "
"cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc42"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.14"
msgid ""
"‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo kodhano kodhahetu abhisaṅgī, ayaṃ me puggalo appiyo "
"amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.15"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho panassaṃ kodhano kodhahetu abhisaṅgī, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ appiyo "
"amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.16"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘na kodhano bhavissāmi na kodhahetu abhisaṅgī’"
"ti cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc43"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.17"
msgid ""
"‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo kodhano kodhasāmantā vācaṃ nicchāretā, ayaṃ me puggalo "
"appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.18"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho panassaṃ kodhano kodhasāmantā vācaṃ nicchāretā, ahampāssaṃ "
"paresaṃ appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.19"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘na kodhano bhavissāmi na kodhasāmantā vācaṃ "
"nicchāressāmī’ti cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.98"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc44"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.20"
msgid ""
"‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo codito codakena codakaṃ paṭippharati, ayaṃ me puggalo "
"appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.21"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho pana codito codakena codakaṃ paṭipphareyyaṃ, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ "
"appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.22"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘codito codakena codakaṃ nappaṭippharissāmī’ti "
"cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc45"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.23"
msgid ""
"‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo codito codakena codakaṃ apasādeti, ayaṃ me puggalo "
"appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.24"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho pana codito codakena codakaṃ apasādeyyaṃ, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ "
"appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.25"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘codito codakena codakaṃ na apasādessāmī’ti "
"cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (8)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc46"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.26"
msgid ""
"‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo codito codakena codakassa paccāropeti, ayaṃ me puggalo "
"appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.27"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho pana codito codakena codakassa paccāropeyyaṃ, ahampāssaṃ "
"paresaṃ appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.28"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘codito codakena codakassa na paccāropessāmī’"
"ti cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (9)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc47"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.29"
msgid ""
"‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo codito codakena aññenaññaṃ paṭicarati, bahiddhā kathaṃ "
"apanāmeti, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti, ayaṃ me puggalo appiyo "
"amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.30"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho pana codito codakena aññenaññaṃ paṭicareyyaṃ, bahiddhā kathaṃ "
"apanāmeyyaṃ, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukareyyaṃ, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ "
"appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.31"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘codito codakena na aññenaññaṃ paṭicarissāmi, "
"na bahiddhā kathaṃ apanāmessāmi, na kopañca dosañca appaccayañca "
"pātukarissāmī’ti cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (10)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc48"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.32"
msgid ""
"‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo codito codakena apadāne na sampāyati, ayaṃ me puggalo "
"appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.33"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho pana codito codakena apadāne na sampāyeyyaṃ, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ "
"appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.34"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘codito codakena apadāne sampāyissāmī’ti "
"cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (11)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc49"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.35"
msgid "‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo makkhī paḷāsī, ayaṃ me puggalo appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.36"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho panassaṃ makkhī paḷāsī, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.37"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘amakkhī bhavissāmi apaḷāsī’ti cittaṃ "
"uppādetabbaṃ. (12)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc50"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.38"
msgid "‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo issukī maccharī, ayaṃ me puggalo appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.39"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho panassaṃ issukī maccharī, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.40"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘anissukī bhavissāmi amaccharī’ti cittaṃ "
"uppādetabbaṃ. (13)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc51"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.41"
msgid "‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo saṭho māyāvī, ayaṃ me puggalo appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.42"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho panassaṃ saṭho māyāvī, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.43"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘asaṭho bhavissāmi amāyāvī’ti cittaṃ "
"uppādetabbaṃ. (14)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc52"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.44"
msgid "‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo thaddho atimānī, ayaṃ me puggalo appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.45"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho panassaṃ thaddho atimānī, ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:6.46"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘atthaddho bhavissāmi anatimānī’ti cittaṃ "
"uppādetabbaṃ. (15)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc53"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:6.47"
msgid ""
"‘Yo khvāyaṃ puggalo sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī ādhānaggāhī duppaṭinissaggī, ayaṃ me "
"puggalo appiyo amanāpo;"
msgstr ""
"‘This person is attached to their own views, holding them tight and refusing "
"to let go. And I don’t like or approve of this person."

msgctxt "mn15:6.48"
msgid ""
"ahañceva kho panassaṃ sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī ādhānaggāhī duppaṭinissaggī, "
"ahampāssaṃ paresaṃ appiyo amanāpo’ti."
msgstr ""
"And if I were to be attached to my own views, holding them tight and "
"refusing to let go, others wouldn’t like or approve of me.’"

msgctxt "mn15:6.49"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ jānantenāvuso, bhikkhunā ‘asandiṭṭhiparāmāsī bhavissāmi anādhānaggāhī "
"suppaṭinissaggī’ti cittaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. (16)"
msgstr ""
"A mendicant who knows this should give rise to the thought: ‘I will not be "
"attached to my own views, holding them tight, but will let them go easily.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc54"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.1"
msgid "Tatrāvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "In such a case, a mendicant should reflect on themselves like this:"

msgctxt "mn15:7.2"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi pāpiccho, pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gato’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘Do I have wicked desires? Have I fallen under the sway of wicked desires?’"

msgctxt "mn15:7.3"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "Suppose that, upon reflection, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn15:7.4"
msgid ""
"‘pāpiccho khomhi, pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gato’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā "
"tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"they have fallen under the sway of wicked desires. Then they should make an "
"effort to give up those bad, unskillful qualities."

msgctxt "mn15:7.5"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "But suppose that, upon reflection, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn15:7.6"
msgid ""
"‘na khomhi pāpiccho, na pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gato’ti, tenāvuso, "
"bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu "
"dhammesu. (1)"
msgstr ""
"they haven’t fallen under the sway of wicked desires. Then they should "
"meditate with rapture and joy, training day and night in skillful qualities. "
"…"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.99"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc55"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.7"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.8"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi attukkaṃsako paravambhī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.9"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.10"
msgid ""
"‘attukkaṃsako khomhi paravambhī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ "
"akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.11"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.12"
msgid ""
"‘anattukkaṃsako khomhi aparavambhī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva "
"pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc56"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.13"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.14"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi kodhano kodhābhibhūto’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.15"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.16"
msgid ""
"‘kodhano khomhi kodhābhibhūto’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ "
"akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.17"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.18"
msgid ""
"‘na khomhi kodhano kodhābhibhūto’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva "
"pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc57"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.19"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.20"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi kodhano kodhahetu upanāhī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.21"
msgid ""
"Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti ‘kodhano khomhi kodhahetu "
"upanāhī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.22"
msgid ""
"Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti ‘na khomhi kodhano "
"kodhahetu upanāhī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ "
"ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc58"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.23"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.24"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi kodhano kodhahetu abhisaṅgī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.25"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.26"
msgid ""
"‘kodhano khomhi kodhahetu abhisaṅgī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva "
"pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.27"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.28"
msgid ""
"‘na khomhi kodhano kodhahetu abhisaṅgī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva "
"pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc59"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.29"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.30"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi kodhano kodhasāmantā vācaṃ nicchāretā’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.31"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.32"
msgid ""
"‘kodhano khomhi kodhasāmantā vācaṃ nicchāretā’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā "
"tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.33"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.34"
msgid ""
"‘na khomhi kodhano kodhasāmantā vācaṃ nicchāretā’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā "
"teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc60"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.35"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.36"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi codito codakena codakaṃ paṭippharāmī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.37"
msgid ""
"Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti ‘codito khomhi codakena "
"codakaṃ paṭippharāmī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.38"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.39"
msgid ""
"‘codito khomhi codakena codakaṃ nappaṭippharāmī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā "
"teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc61"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.40"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.41"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi codito codakena codakaṃ apasādemī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.42"
msgid ""
"Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti ‘codito khomhi codakena "
"codakaṃ apasādemī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.43"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.44"
msgid ""
"‘codito khomhi codakena codakaṃ na apasādemī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva "
"pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (8)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc62"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.45"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.46"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi codito codakena codakassa paccāropemī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.47"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.48"
msgid ""
"‘codito khomhi codakena codakassa paccāropemī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā "
"tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.49"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.50"
msgid ""
"‘codito khomhi codakena codakassa na paccāropemī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā "
"teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (9)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc63"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.51"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.52"
msgid ""
"‘kiṃ nu khomhi codito codakena aññenaññaṃ paṭicarāmi, bahiddhā kathaṃ "
"apanāmemi, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaromī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.53"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.54"
msgid ""
"‘codito khomhi codakena aññenaññaṃ paṭicarāmi, bahiddhā kathaṃ apanāmemi, "
"kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaromī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva "
"pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.55"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.56"
msgid ""
"‘codito khomhi codakena na aññenaññaṃ paṭicarāmi, na bahiddhā kathaṃ "
"apanāmemi, na kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaromī’ti, tenāvuso, "
"bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu "
"dhammesu. (10)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc64"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.57"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.58"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi codito codakena apadāne na sampāyāmī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.59"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.60"
msgid ""
"‘codito khomhi codakena apadāne na sampāyāmī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā "
"tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.61"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.62"
msgid ""
"‘codito khomhi codakena apadāne sampāyāmī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva "
"pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (11)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc65"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.63"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.64"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi makkhī paḷāsī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.65"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.66"
msgid ""
"‘makkhī khomhi paḷāsī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.67"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.68"
msgid ""
"‘amakkhī khomhi apaḷāsī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena "
"vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (12)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc66"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.69"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.70"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi issukī maccharī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.71"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.72"
msgid ""
"‘issukī khomhi maccharī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ "
"akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.73"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.74"
msgid ""
"‘anissukī khomhi amaccharī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena "
"vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (13)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc67"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.75"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.76"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi saṭho māyāvī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.77"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.78"
msgid ""
"‘saṭho khomhi māyāvī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.79"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.80"
msgid ""
"‘asaṭho khomhi amāyāvī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena "
"vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (14)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc68"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.81"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.82"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi thaddho atimānī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.83"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.84"
msgid ""
"‘thaddho khomhi atimānī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ "
"akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.85"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.86"
msgid ""
"‘atthaddho khomhi anatimānī’ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena "
"vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu. (15)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.100"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc69"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:7.87"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.88"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu khomhi sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī ādhānaggāhī duppaṭinissaggī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn15:7.89"
msgid "Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "Suppose that, upon reflection, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn15:7.90"
msgid ""
"‘sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī khomhi ādhānaggāhī duppaṭinissaggī’ti, tenāvuso, "
"bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"they are attached to their own views, holding them tight, and refusing to "
"let go. Then they should make an effort to give up those bad, unskillful "
"qualities."

msgctxt "mn15:7.91"
msgid "Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "Suppose that, upon reflection, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn15:7.92"
msgid ""
"‘asandiṭṭhiparāmāsī khomhi anādhānaggāhī suppaṭinissaggī’ti, tenāvuso, "
"bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu "
"dhammesu. (16)"
msgstr ""
"they’re not attached to their own views, holding them tight, but let them go "
"easily. Then they should meditate with rapture and joy, training day and "
"night in skillful qualities."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc70"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:8.1"
msgid ""
"Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale dhamme "
"appahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā sabbesaṃyeva imesaṃ "
"pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Suppose that, upon reflection, a mendicant sees that they haven’t given up "
"all these bad, unskillful qualities. Then they should make an effort to give "
"them all up."

msgctxt "mn15:8.2"
msgid ""
"Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale dhamme "
"pahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena "
"vihātabbaṃ, ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"But suppose that, upon reflection, a mendicant sees that they have given up "
"all these bad, unskillful qualities. Then they should meditate with rapture "
"and joy, training day and night in skillful qualities."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc71"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:8.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, āvuso, itthī vā puriso vā, daharo yuvā maṇḍanajātiko, ādāse vā "
"parisuddhe pariyodāte, acche vā udakapatte, sakaṃ mukhanimittaṃ "
"paccavekkhamāno, sace tattha passati rajaṃ vā aṅgaṇaṃ vā, tasseva rajassa vā "
"aṅgaṇassa vā pahānāya vāyamati;"
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a woman or man who was young, youthful, and fond of "
"adornments, and they check their own reflection in a clean bright mirror or "
"a clear bowl of water. If they see any dirt or blemish there, they’d try to "
"remove it."

msgctxt "mn15:8.4"
msgid "no ce tattha passati rajaṃ vā aṅgaṇaṃ vā, teneva attamano hoti:"
msgstr ""
"But if they don’t see any dirt or blemish there, they’re happy, thinking:"

msgctxt "mn15:8.5"
msgid "‘lābhā vata me, parisuddhaṃ vata me’ti."
msgstr "‘How fortunate that I’m clean!’"

msgctxt "mn15:8.6"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, āvuso, sace bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale "
"dhamme appahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā sabbesaṃyeva "
"imesaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, suppose that, upon reflection, a mendicant sees that they "
"haven’t given up all these bad, unskillful qualities. Then they should make "
"an effort to give them all up."

msgctxt "mn15:8.7"
msgid ""
"Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale dhamme "
"pahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena "
"vihātabbaṃ, ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesū”ti."
msgstr ""
"But suppose that, upon reflection, a mendicant sees that they have given up "
"all these bad, unskillful qualities. Then they should meditate with rapture "
"and joy, training day and night in skillful qualities.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc72"></a>
msgctxt "mn15:8.8"
msgid "Idamavocāyasmā mahāmoggallāno."
msgstr "This is what Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said."

msgctxt "mn15:8.9"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr ""
"Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn15:8.10"
msgid "Anumānasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
